Introduction

JEY is a Korean-Australian singer under ALFHA and a part of FA Crew. He debuted as a soloist in 2017 under S.F.R Entertainment. He was a member of ambitious ambition but left the crew. He was a former trainee of YG Entertainment & KQ Produce, best known for competing in the survival show "MIX&MATCH" that formed the group iKON.
